channel.title: Workstation: tor circuit not established
channel.description:
Running virtualbox 6.1 Gateway: fully updated and running, (stable repo) whonixcheck all green
Workstation: whonixcheck gives up with: - Tor circuit: not established - Timesync status: not done - sdwdate reports: Prerequisite check not done yet
sdwdate log: INFO clock is sane WARNING Tor is not yet fully bootstrapped. Tor circuit: not established
any idea what i can try ?
